===============================================================================

Some setup you must do manually:

  1. Modify captcha images directory in config/initializers/fancy_captcha.rb.
     For example:

       config.images_path = Rails.root.join("public", "captcha_images").to_s

  2. Generate captcha images.

       # bundle exec rake fancy_captcha:generate_images[100]


Homepage: https://github.com/vkill/fancy_captcha
by: vkill
===============================================================================

